            <title>[SOLR-520] o.a.s.analysis.LengthFilter should be deprecated</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-520</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;According to:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.nabble.com/WordDelimiterFilter%2BLenghtFilter-results-in-termPosition%3D%3D-1-td16306788.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://www.nabble.com/WordDelimiterFilter%2BLenghtFilter-results-in-termPosition%3D%3D-1-td16306788.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

